{"tid":301342,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[眼紅者勿入][Nintendo Switch]買機x報價x放骨x鋪頭撚狗交流中心[26]","createTime":"2017-06-28T14:26:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T16:07:48.000Z","uid":59888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bc7faa7b79c3eba9e59a26f9e49f9143d64f4a5d","tid":301342,"uid":59888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T14:26:45.000Z","msg":"炒家死全家"},{"pid":"8b6398fedef5a1565fc3eebf229e8098d9d7f684","tid":301342,"uid":59888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T14:27:34.000Z","msg":"堅守正價領域 炒狗全家乞食 Q&amp;A<br />\n<br />\nQ1. 點解一定要正價買switch?<br />\n<br />\n好簡單 我同你講 原本＄2340買到既野 你會唔會用$2341去買？<br />\n唔會囉 因為$2341-$2340 ＝$1<br />\n如果都係唔明 麻煩你耷低個頭開個計算機apps計下你就知<br />\n打機係為開心 如果要蝕錢不如唔好打<br />\n<br />\nQ2. 炒狗點影響個市場？<br />\n<br />\n細鋪炒狗一個二個聯合起上黎 事實力量係勁過大鋪甚至上市公司 <br />\n例如兇宅 so0 百記 佢地炒起個市搞到全世界都無switch賣<br />\n全球間間店鋪都strong hold 真係好可恥 如果幫襯佢地等於助長炒風<br />\n遊戲業比你搞彎晒<br />\n<br />\nQ3. 除左等，依家有咩可以做？<br />\n<br />\n我地可以搞網上抗爭 首先從連登做起 <br />\n再搵埋議員 長毛 熱狗佢地一定撐硬我地<br />\n搞場街上抗議 要做到革命咁款 為我地下一代既正價switch 謀福址"},{"pid":"73033ac4c1724630a02173f3bd85a66b25c0a6c6","tid":301342,"uid":120852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T14:29:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e7e4df6cfc660d38b7ce9941aaf3b97a49d6dae","tid":301342,"uid":8141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T14:30:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4d44326bf3aea51627c2028e9c73ec3eaaa056","tid":301342,"uid":8659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T14:35:17.000Z","msg":"假膠文就咪撚貼啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dadc4b760b53a3db475799e87984c9623c1158c","tid":301342,"uid":124606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T15:05:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"